{"tid":1380530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係要申請定只係通知呀？","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:21.000Z","uid":286966,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8964668eafc232f228d4991a962d8695fe751aaf","tid":1380530,"uid":286966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200010/10/1010251.htm?fbclid=IwAR3uQje5sxghJsrj3092lZiARr7jBW2elbtUfb2Wmxbmb6UTX-RDmF-AmNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200010%2F10%2F1010251.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3uQje5sxghJsrj3092lZiARr7jBW2elbtUfb2Wmxbmb6UTX-RDmF-AmNw&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67ZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=35677661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200010/10/1010251.htm?fbclid=IwAR3uQje5sxghJsrj3092lZiARr7jBW2elbtUfb2Wmxbmb6UTX-RDmF-AmNw</a><br />\n<br />\n公眾遊行不需申請牌照<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（十月十日）指出，根據現行《公安條例》，三十人以上的公眾遊行毋須事先向警方申請牌照。主辦者只須於七日前通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於有批評指現時主辦者必須於收到警方的「不反對通知書」後方可舉行遊行，並謂此乃一變相的申請牌照制度，發言人說這純屬誤解。<br />\n............<br />\n<br />\n二○○○年十月十日（星期二）"},{"pid":"324be6b412303705ae2014dc8d7dcc8b33b3dcde","tid":1380530,"uid":286966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"自己推下先"},{"pid":"a32235701907b4c0a66db53137e6ba48f4dbca73","tid":1380530,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd69c5711dab9606bca37eaaa3201af6d450f07c","tid":1380530,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"毅進警察 社會垃圾<br />\n畜蟲小隊 冚家富貴"},{"pid":"eb379722f13eb7ba2c2a59e70c16cbd7744aba29","tid":1380530,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe5bd5eb270e81377723d2b4d8e287e9187bc063","tid":1380530,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci